With due respect, please try to do the following to make this discussion fruitful (and before spamming Bugzilla with further patches):

1. Read comment #1 in its entirety and make sure you address all mentioned issues;
2. Consider if you still want to convert the port to use GitHub now that it was fixed for the time being as of ports r422350;
3. Actually perform "make clean all check-plist" with proposed patch(es) applied (successfully, that is).
